---
// P-01 [H-3] ソリューション・トリアージ (BPO vs SaaS)
---

<section class="py-20 sm:py-28 lg:py-32 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-blue-50/30">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 sm:mb-20 lg:mb-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-[1.15] tracking-tight">
        あなたの課題に最適な解決策は、
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-gray-600">
        どちらですか？
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- BPO Card -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100/80 rounded-3xl p-10 sm:p-12 border-2 border-blue-200 hover:border-blue-400 transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl group hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 leading-tight">
            Full-Funnel<br class="hidden sm:block" /> Partner
          </h3>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-5 mb-10">
          <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-blue-100 shadow-md">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 text-lg">対象</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">大企業・新規事業部門向け</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-blue-100 shadow-md">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 text-lg">価値</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">戦略立案から実行まで「伴走支援」</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700 hover:from-blue-700 hover:to-blue-800 text-white font-bold py-4 sm:py-5 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 text-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98]">
          BPOサービス詳細へ →
        </button>
      </div>

      <!-- SaaS Card -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-purple-100/80 rounded-3xl p-10 sm:p-12 border-2 border-purple-200 hover:border-purple-400 transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl group hover:-translate-y-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 to-purple-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-9 h-9 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 leading-tight">
            Full-Funnel<br class="hidden sm:block" /> Partner AI
          </h3>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-5 mb-10">
          <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-purple-100 shadow-md">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 text-lg">対象</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">中小企業・スタートアップ向け</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-purple-100 shadow-md">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 text-lg">価値</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">AIでコンテンツ制作を「内製化・効率化」</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-purple-700 hover:from-purple-700 hover:to-purple-800 text-white font-bold py-4 sm:py-5 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 text-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98]">
          SaaSサービス詳細へ →
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

